text: a l laoh ban banhchouh peakyapech da laobrapei chea kompir ( kuor an) del( ayeat robsa vea) braheak brahel knea sa choh sa laeng . sbek robsa banda anak del kaotakhlach mcheasa robsa puokke pru nheabnhr daoysaar vea( nowpel ban sdablyy khlea teangnih) . banteab mk sbek robsa puokke ning chetd robsa puokke nungonr tnphlon chhpaohtow rk kar romluk robsa a l laoh . noh haey kuchea kar changaoulobangheanh robsa a l laoh del trong changaoulobangheanh tamory vea dl anaknea del trong mean chetnea . haey anaknea del a l laoh thveu aoy v nge vng ku kmean anak na mneak changaoulobangheanh dl ke laey
